  <h2>Getting Started</h2>

  <h3>Download the App</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fieldpromax.fieldpromaxplus" target="_blank">Google Play Store (Android)</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/in/app/field-promax-plus/id6446847200" target="_blank">Apple App Store (iOS)</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Login</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>Your password was emailed to you when your account was created</li>
    <li>Check your SPAM folder if you didn't receive it, or contact your administrator</li>
    <li>Log in using your <strong>email and password</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Work Order Views</h2>
  <img src="/images/mobile-app/overview_01.jpg" alt="Work Order Views" />
  <p>View work orders in three different formats:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Tile View:</strong> Organizes work orders in a list format</li>
    <li><strong>Calendar View:</strong> Displays work orders by dispatched date</li>
    <li><strong>Map View:</strong> Shows work orders based on location</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>User Access</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Administrators:</strong> Have access to all work orders</li>
    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Only see work orders assigned to them</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Dashboard</h2>
  <img src="/images/mobile-app/overview_02.jpg" alt="Mobile Dashboard" />
  <p>Work orders in Tile View are organized by timeframe:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Today's Work Orders:</strong> Dispatched for the current day</li>
    <li><strong>Tomorrow's Work Orders:</strong> Dispatched for the next day</li>
    <li><strong>Upcoming Work Orders:</strong> Future work orders beyond tomorrow</li>
    <li><strong>Unassigned Orders:</strong> Work orders not yet assigned to a technician</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Tap the <strong>right arrow</strong> next to a work order to open and review details.</p>

  <h2>Dashboard Menu</h2>
  <img src="/images/mobile-app/overview_03.jpg" alt="Dashboard Menu" />
  <p>Access the menu from the top left to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Create Work Orders</li>
    <li>Create Estimates</li>
    <li>Create Customers</li>
    <li>Manage Timecards</li>
    <li>Submit Expense Receipts</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Notifications</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Technicians receive <strong>text and email notifications</strong> when assigned to work orders</li>
    <li><strong>Reminder notifications</strong> ensure jobs are completed on time</li>
    <li>When a technician taps <strong>In Route</strong>, the customer receives an automated text message</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Tips</h2>
  <div class="callout callout-tip">
    <p>
      <strong>Tap the refresh button</strong> at the top right to update your work order list.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Use the menu for quick access</strong> to create work orders, estimates, and customers efficiently.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong>Expand work order sections</strong> to stay organized and see categorized work orders.
    </p>
  </div>
